sequenceDiagram
    participant App as Application
    participant Store as VectorStore
    participant Client as Backend Client<br/>(e.g., qdrant.Client)
    participant Backend as Vector Database<br/>(e.g., Qdrant Server)

    Note over App,Backend: Connection Phase

    App->>Store: NewClient(config)
    Store-->>App: *Client, nil

    App->>Store: Connect(ctx)
    Store->>Client: mu.Lock()
    Client->>Backend: Health check request
    Backend-->>Client: 200 OK
    Client->>Client: connected = true
    Store->>Client: mu.Unlock()
    Store-->>App: nil

    Note over App,Backend: Collection Setup

    App->>Store: CreateCollection(ctx, config)
    Store->>Client: mu.RLock()
    Client->>Client: Check connected == true
    Client->>Client: config.Validate()
    Client->>Backend: Create collection request
    Backend-->>Client: Success response
    Store->>Client: mu.RUnlock()
    Store-->>App: nil

    Note over App,Backend: Upsert Phase

    App->>Store: Upsert(ctx, collection, vectors)
    Store->>Client: mu.RLock()
    Client->>Client: Check connected == true
    Client->>Client: Check vectors not empty
    Client->>Client: Auto-generate UUIDs for empty IDs
    Client->>Backend: Upsert request (JSON)
    Backend-->>Client: Success response
    Store->>Client: mu.RUnlock()
    Store-->>App: nil

    Note over App,Backend: Search Phase

    App->>Store: Search(ctx, collection, query)
    Store->>Client: mu.RLock()
    Client->>Client: Check connected == true
    Client->>Backend: Search request (vector, topK, filter)
    Backend-->>Client: Results (id, score, metadata)
    Client->>Client: Parse response
    Client->>Client: Apply MinScore filter (if needed)
    Client->>Client: Map to []SearchResult
    Store->>Client: mu.RUnlock()
    Store-->>App: []SearchResult, nil

    Note over App,Backend: Retrieval Phase

    App->>Store: Get(ctx, collection, ids)
    Store->>Client: mu.RLock()
    Client->>Client: Check connected == true
    Client->>Client: Check ids not empty
    Client->>Backend: Get by IDs request
    Backend-->>Client: Vectors with metadata
    Client->>Client: Map to []Vector
    Store->>Client: mu.RUnlock()
    Store-->>App: []Vector, nil

    Note over App,Backend: Deletion Phase

    App->>Store: Delete(ctx, collection, ids)
    Store->>Client: mu.RLock()
    Client->>Client: Check connected == true
    Client->>Client: Check ids not empty
    Client->>Backend: Delete request
    Backend-->>Client: Success response
    Store->>Client: mu.RUnlock()
    Store-->>App: nil

    Note over App,Backend: Cleanup Phase

    App->>Store: Close()
    Store->>Client: mu.Lock()
    Client->>Client: connected = false
    Client->>Client: Release resources
    Store->>Client: mu.Unlock()
    Store-->>App: nil
